title: Kill Hannah - Discography (1996 - 2007) [mp3@VBR]
description:
Kill Hannah is an alternative rock band formed in Chicago, Illinois and is currently signed to Roadrunner Records.
Kill Hannah was formed by singer-songwriter Mat Devine in 1994. The band is named after Devine&#039;s ex-girlfriend. 
Devine was singing and playing guitar in a band called "In a Jar UK". After the fallout with Hannah, Devine printed up stickers to place on "In a Jar UK" 7" records bearing the name "Kill Hannah".

more on: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kill_Hannah
